{"tid":1532720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部：香港遊行示威已演化為極端暴力行動","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:16:59.000Z","uid":68738,"like":32,"dislike":199,"uniUserReply":134,"replies":[{"pid":"af79b90c81d36b0d8e278758e1a3e26120e32d2b","tid":1532720,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"人民日報消息，今天，外交部回應歐盟政客涉港不當言論，耿爽表示，當前在香港發生的遊行示威活動已經完全超出了集會遊行示威自由的範疇，已經演化為極端的暴力行動，嚴重挑戰了香港的法治和社會秩序，嚴重威脅到香港市民的生命財產安全，也嚴重觸犯了一國兩制的原則底線。如此嚴重的暴力違法罪行，如果發生在歐洲，相信任何一個歐洲國家都不會坐視不管。我們希望歐方能夠明辨是非，理解和支持香港特區政府依法止暴制亂，維護香港的法治和繁榮穩定。"},{"pid":"439a446a55522e9c9e83ba10a5c5a078136b97ea","tid":1532720,"uid":94454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:04:25.000Z","msg":"okok"},{"pid":"504170c8d750ae69ba2775f842a9bce09153bb0f","tid":1532720,"uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2803301701/4412112631614772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2F2803301701%2F4412112631614772&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ao6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=67ba2b47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/2803301701/4412112631614772</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd82ffeb761b5cbb85b7709e840e88dfce59d1b","tid":1532720,"uid":47311,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"一見到佢就諗起<br />\n<br />\n爽死了~~~爽死了"},{"pid":"4a643ced1db09d7aa05505c3480fa6cbf3df4cd9","tid":1532720,"uid":58164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6884bd611470917599656187e4a70228833ef8f6","tid":1532720,"uid":224479,"l